linux开发环境依赖安装：<BR>
<b>yum</b> install gcc gcc-c++ gcc-g77 flex bison autoconf automake bzip2-devel  zlib-devel ncurses-devel libjpeg-devel libpng-devel libtiff-devel freetype-devel pam-devel openssl-devel libxml2-devel gettext-devel  pcre-devel mysql-devel net-snmp-devel curl-devel perl-DBI<BR>
