一句话安装lamp：<BR>
<b>yum</b> -y install gcc gcc-c++ gcc-g77 flex bison autoconf automake  bzip2-devel zlib-devel ncurses-devel libjpeg-devel libpng-devel libtiff-devel freetype-devel pam-devel openssl-devel libxml2-devel gettext-devel  pcre-devel mysql-devel net-snmp-devel curl-devel perl-DBI mysql mysql-server httpd php php-mysql php-gd php-imap php-ldap php-odbc php-pear php-xml php-xmlrpc  php-bcmath php-mbstring 
</DD>
